title: Top 500 Foreclosure Zipcodes , USA
name: Top 500 Foreclosure Zipcodes , USA
description: This dataset shows the top 500 zip codes for home foreclosures, along with bank repossessions, default and auction notices. Most of the foreclosures seem to be in thje rust belt and the sun belt. This data was found online at: http://money.cnn.com/2007/06/19/real_estate/500_top_foreclosure_zip_codes/index.htmI was only able to successfully geo-locate 481 of the top 500 zip codes.
